SELECT users.full_name, user_roles.role_name, access_logs.access_time FROM users JOIN user_roles ON users.user_id = user_roles.user_id JOIN access_logs ON users.user_id = access_logs.user_id WHERE access_logs.access_result = 'SUCCESS' AND user_roles.role_name = 'Admin' ORDER BY access_logs.access_time DESC LIMIT 10;
